            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>Flamma, a secutor [gladiator] lived for 30 years, fought 34 times, won 21 times, drew 9 times, was defeated [spared] 4 times. Syrian by nationality. Delicatus built this for a worthy comrade-at-arms</p>
